description: Counts of samples and donors in a sample (sub)collection
Sample collection the count belongs to.
The sex of the individuals in the fact. Can be one of the following values: Male, Female, Unknown, Undifferrentiated, Not applicable.
Age group of the sample donors at time of sample donation.
The biospecimen saved from a biological entity for propagation e.g. testing, diagnostics, treatment or research purposes.
The disease or disease category of main interest in the collection, if any - MIABIS-COLLECTION-16 (v3.0)
